(26848, 25043, 0, 1, 'Samurai slave driver', '描寫二戰時亞洲蠻橫的日本帝國 , 將戰俘關在台灣 . 迫使美軍轟炸台北城 . \r\n\r\n我們站在無法立足的立場上 . 希望美軍能趕走日本人 . 但也摧殘了我們的國土 . \r\n\r\n解救了戰俘 . 日軍也撤回 .  台灣不在是殖民地 . 但是創傷已留下在每個台灣人心中', '2010-07-25 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 9, 'Samurai Slave driver\r\n\r\nWorld War II, Scourge upon the earth\r\nJapanese Occupation, reign of tyranny\r\nDown in the mines, the prisoners of war\r\n\r\nBomb us and we drown your men,\r\nDare us and they die\r\nBomb us and we drown your men,\r\n Dare us and they die\r\n(Operation, operation)\r\nSamurai Slave driver\r\n\r\nWar of attrition, die of exhaustion \r\nHeat, sweat, dehydration\r\nDown in the mines, the prisoners of war\r\n\r\n\r\nBomb us and we drown your men,\r\nDare us and they die\r\nBomb us and we drown your men,\r\n Dare us and they die\r\n(Operation, operation)\r\nSamurai Slave driver\r\n\r\n\r\nHeat, sweat, dehydration\r\nDown in the mines, the prisoners of war\r\n\r\n  Return home, scared forever\r\nThe prisoners of war\r\nWe are all prisoners of war\r\n\r\nThe katana falls\r\nSamurai Slave driver(x3)\r\n', '', 260, '', '鳥/Masquerader', '老外', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2010-07-25 00:33:31', '2013-10-07 17:16:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(26849, 62631, 0, 1, 'my kind of girl (demo 2010)', '', '2010-07-25 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, 'you know your way to be a mystery, naturally\r\nyou''ve got a style that''s never showed, on any magazine\r\nyou write your cover stories, on my pages, with every look you give\r\nyeah you''ve got a hold on me, with your kind of magic, god I just can''t help myself\r\n\r\nmy eyes go fuzzy\r\nyou let my butterflies, flying\r\n\r\nyou are my kind of girl\r\noh no\r\noh god I''m losing all control\r\n\r\nyea you are my kind of girl\r\noh yes\r\nI''m losing it all, from top to my toe\r\n\r\nI have kept away all the other cats\r\nsomehow they make me distracted, I just don’t think it’s right\r\nI know it''s crazy, you ask me "why?" I''m so dumb. Baby I don''t know why\r\nI feel I''m going off the wire. getting drunk in your wine, still I just can''t help myself\r\n\r\ncolors in my sky\r\nyou really set my butterflies flying high\r\n\r\nyou are my kind of girl\r\noh yeah\r\nif love is a crime, do me this wrong\r\nbe the bringer of this evil\r\n\r\nyou are my kind of girl\r\noh babe\r\nplease let me know\r\nis there any hope for me to take you home\r\n\r\n(instrumental)\r\nthere''s one thing in this world i know for sure\r\nand I, I want you to know\r\n\r\nyou are my kind of girl\r\nif love is a crime, it''s all my fault\r\nbut you''re that little devil\r\n\r\nyou are my kind of girl\r\noh babe\r\njust give me your hand\r\nthere will be no remorse\r\njust believe this stupid miracle\r\n\r\nif you are my kind girl', '', 297, '', '降落傘', '思達', '陳佑', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2010-07-25 01:36:09', '2015-03-12 13:43:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(26850, 62631, 0, 1, 'leopard''s heart (demo)', '動物星球頻道說獵豹如果一直狂追獵物追不上, 體溫過高會有生命危險\r\n但是台灣人是獵豹之子, 獵豹爸爸心臟過熱, 我們是肝臟過熱\r\n在死之前都全力衝刺吧！', '2010-07-25 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 4, 'I''ve been thinking, but I just can''t figure it out\r\nwith this freedom why don''t we stop being pushed around\r\nwe sure are free enough to go for what we really want\r\nso why do we still look away from the brightest star?\r\n\r\nwe have it all to get it done\r\nso stop finding things to blame your difficulties on\r\n\r\naim at the toughest mark\r\nfor the gold award of this hunt\r\nyou gotta show your leopard''s heart\r\n(leopard''s heart)\r\n\r\ndon''t say you can''t go on\r\nstand up, back in the run\r\nkeep doing it right then there could be no wrong\r\n\r\na leopard''s heart\r\nnever stops\r\n\r\nI did my thinking, but it''s hard to figure it out\r\nall the wisdom only led us to the most crowded route\r\nthey say the time is tough, but you know that''s not excuse for giving up\r\nchances may be thin but a hero won''t back down\r\n\r\njust be prepared for your time to come\r\nso that things could work out for you somehow\r\n\r\naim at the toughest mark\r\nfor the gold award of this hunt\r\nyou gotta show your leopard''s heart\r\n\r\ndon''t say you can''t go on\r\nstand up, back in the run\r\nwhen you go, you go at it hard\r\n\r\ncoz leopard''s heart\r\nrun up front\r\n\r\nall the heroes have their flaws\r\nall the stories have lost a part\r\nsituations could be tough\r\nbut some people carry on\r\nno matter who you are\r\njust show them what you are\r\n\r\naim at the toughest mark\r\nfor the gold award of this hunt\r\nyou gotta show your leopard''s heart\r\n\r\ndon''t say you can''t go on\r\nstand up, back in the run\r\nso you can burn the world with your blood\r\n\r\na leopard''s heart\r\nrunning hard\r\n\r\n(gotta show me your leopard''s heart)\r\n(on your run cannot be stopped, oh yeah)', '', 236, '', 'Yu Chen', 'Star Lee', 'the Parachutes', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2010-07-25 01:37:08', '2013-10-07 17:16:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(26851, 62631, 0, 1, 'keep it fresh (demo 2010)', '', '2010-07-25 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, 'there was this special friend I had\r\nshe''s like a little sister of mine \r\nwe talked about every black and white\r\nnight after night\r\n\r\nbut since she went serious with a guy\r\nshe talks bad about him all the time\r\ngirl if you are not asking my advices\r\ntell me what do you expect?\r\n\r\nshould I be jealous like people in the movies\r\nwhen they are where we''re at\r\nbut all these talkings about your bad romance\r\nonly make me feel sick and tired\r\n\r\nhey girl there''s something you need to realize\r\nnot every relationship''s good to take next step\r\ngood friends is what we are, nothing more or less\r\ndon''t try to make a mess, just keep it where it''s at\r\n\r\nkeep it fresh\r\n\r\nit''s easy to say baby don''t cry\r\nit''s easy to say i like your smile\r\nbut you know once those magic be cast\r\nthere''ll be no turning back\r\n\r\nnever a doubt in my mind\r\nthat you deserve better than that guy\r\nbut for whatever reason\r\nI don''t want to change what''s between you and I\r\n\r\nis it so hard to be satisfied without that\r\nchili spice\r\nwhy can''t we leave it as a little dish of life\r\ndon''t risk losing our appetite\r\n\r\nhey girl there''s something you need to realize\r\nnot every relationship''s good to take next step\r\ngood friendship that we have is hard to find\r\ndon''t try to make a mess, let''s keep it where it''s at\r\n\r\nkeep it fresh\r\n\r\n(instrumental)\r\n\r\nwhen it comes to love we all get polarized\r\nforgetting about how to share not to fight\r\ncannot un-break the hearts you know they are all made of glass\r\nso don''t start something that could end up real bad\r\n\r\nhey girl there''s something you need to realize\r\nnot every relationship''s good to take next step\r\nyou need to learn to enjoy this quality time\r\ndon''t try to make a mess, just leave it where it''s at\r\n\r\nlet''s try to keep it fresh', '', 260, '', '降落傘', '思達', '陳佑', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2010-07-25 01:37:56', '2015-03-12 13:43:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
